doc.after: State governments have partially filled the breach left by reductions in federal aid Several states have entered into operating partnerships with Amtrak notably California Pennsylvania Illinois Michigan Oregon Missouri Washington North Carolina Oklahoma Texas Wisconsin Vermont Maine and New York as well as the Canadian province of British Columbia which provides some of the resources for the operation of the Cascades route
